partnerDetails.about: Industrial Automation Systems Integrators providing leading edge Automation Solutions to the Industrial Manufacturing Industry and Security Sector. We engineer solutions including PLC, SCADA, Electrical & Instrumentation and Mechanical components for among others the Food, Utility, Specialist Chemical, Sugar and Security Sectors in South Africa and Internationally.
